text: The Incredible Sarah is a 1976 British period drama movie directed by Richard Fleischer and starring Glenda Jackson, Daniel Massey, Yvonne Mitchell, David Langton, John Castle, Edward Judd and Peter Sallis. It was nominated for two Oscars in 1977. ==Other websites== * Category:1976 drama movies Category:British drama movies Category:Movies directed by Richard Fleischer
